rent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\">1) 제목</span></span></h3><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">회귀분석을 통한 스팸 분류 모델 생성과 검증</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span id=\"2\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\">2) 작성자</span></span></h3><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">가정교육학과 백지현, 국제무역학과 이성민</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span id=\"3\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">3) 링크 및 출처</span></span></h3><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">Practical Data Science with R( Nina Zumel, John Moun)의 PART2의 5단원</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span id=\"4\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">4) 문제 및 개요</span></span></h3><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">스팸 분류 데이터의&nbsp;<b style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">오차행렬</b><b style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">(Confusion matrix)</b>을 만들어보고,</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">회귀분석을 이용한 스팸&nbsp;<b style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">분류</b><b style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">(Classification)</b>&nbsp;모델을 만들고 ROC곡선과 로그-우도(log likelihood)를 통하여 모델을 검증한다.</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"></h3><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span id=\"5\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\">5) 데이터</span></span></h3><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">https://github.com/WinVector/zmPDSwR/tree/master/Spambase<span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">&nbsp;에서&nbsp;</span><b style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">\'spamD.tsv\'</b><b style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">&nbsp;</b><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">데이터를 다운로드 받을 수 있다.<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\"></span><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">spamD.tsv에는 ‘스팸에서 자주 출현하는 48개 주요 단어에 대한 각각의 빈도수 컬럼’ 48개,<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">‘달러, 해시 기호를 포함한 6개 기호의 빈도를 나타내는 컬럼’ 6개,<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">‘주요 run-length(동일데이터 연속길이)의 평균, 최대, 총합을 나타내는 컬럼’ 각 1개씩 총 3개,<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">‘스팸여부 (spam/non-spam) 컬럼’ 1개, ‘rgroup 컬럼’ 1개 까지, 총 59개 컬럼이 있다.</span></span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span id=\"6\" style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">6) 해결방법 및 결과</span></span></h3><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\"><strong style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Listing 5.1</strong>&nbsp;Building and applying a logistic regression spam model</span></em><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(142, 142, 142);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\">&gt; spamD &lt;- read.table(\'spamD.tsv\',header=T,sep=\'t\')</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">&gt; spamTrain &lt;- subset(spamD,spamD$rgroup&gt;=10)<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\"></span><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">&gt; spamTest &lt;- subset(spamD,spamD$rgroup&lt;10)<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\"></span><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 19px;\">&gt; spamVars &lt;- setdiff(colnames(spamD),list(\'rgroup\',\'spam\'))</span></span></p><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">spamD 데이터에서 Train data, Test data를 할당한다.</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(142, 142, 142);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\">&gt; spamFormula &lt;- as.formula(paste(\'spam==\"spam\"\',<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">&gt; paste(spamVars,collapse=\' + \'),sep=\' ~ \'))<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">&gt; spamModel &lt;- glm(spamFormula,family=binomial(link=\'logit\'), data=spamTrain)<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">&gt; spamTrain$pred &lt;- predict(spamModel,newdata=spamTrain, type=\'response\')<br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233);\">&gt; spamTest$pred &lt;- predict(spamModel,newdata=spamTest, type=\'response\')</span></p><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">spamFormula의 변수들에 대하여 glm()함수로 회귀분석을 하여 spamModel에 저장한다.</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); line-height: 19px; font-family: Helvetica;\">predict()함수를 사용하여 회귀 결과를 예측한 값을 spamTrain, spamTest에 각각 pred컬럼에 저장한다.</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(142, 142, 142);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica;\">&gt; print(with(spamTest,table(y=spam,glmPred=pred&gt;0.5)))</span></p><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Helvetica;\">y를 스팸여부로 하고 x의 glmPred는 값이 0.5를 넘기는 것을 체크하여 테이블을 출력한다.</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(142, 142, 142); line-height: 19px; font-family: Helvetica;\">아래 결과와 같은 표를 Confusion Matrix(오차행렬)라 한다. 이는 해당 분류(classifier)의 예측과 실제 데이터 분류를 요약한 것이다.</span><br style=\"border-color: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(142, 142, 142); font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px rgb(233, 233, 233); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: Ubuntu, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(142